    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small, thick drinking glasses without a stem used for serving a measure (shot) of whiskey or other liquor. They traditionally contain 1 1/2 ounces of liquid.</Note_Text>
